"What is this little kid doing here?</i>

167
00:14:08.264 --> 00:14:09.807
<i>He should be in school. you know."</i>

168
00:14:10.391 --> 00:14:13.644
I was so nervous that I'm going
to screw up and have to go home.

169
00:14:14.186 --> 00:14:16.564
<i>That was my biggest fear.</i>

170
00:14:18.023 --> 00:14:23.654
<i>And then one day in the middle of lunch.
