192
00:16:06.799 --> 00:16:09.176
I'm gonna go back tomorrow
and see what happens.

193
00:16:15.307 --> 00:16:19.937
<i>The next morning at 6:30 a.m..
I went back to the hotel.</i>

194
00:16:22.022 --> 00:16:24.817
