00:33:47.358 --> 00:33:49.068
<i>and an unlisted phone number.</i>

427
00:33:49.152 --> 00:33:51.529
<i>It's one of Tinseltown's
hottest lunch spots.</i>

428
00:33:51.612 --> 00:33:54.824
<i>and nobody cares if the dining area
is a former parking lot.</i>

429
00:33:54.907 --> 00:33:56.451
<i>covered with Astroturf.</i>

430
00:33:56.534 --> 00:33:59.662
<i>It's so popular
that jetsetters jockey for a table.</i>

431
00:33:59.746 --> 00:34:02.749
<i>and everyone wants to make friends
with the waiters.</i>

432
00:34:04.375 --> 00:34:06.836
WOLFGANG: <i>Working at Ma Maison was crazy.</i>

433
00:34:06.919 --> 00:34:08.588
So right now. with my lobster.

434
00:34:08.671 --> 00:34:12.091
WOLFGANG: <i>I would wake up early.
